    <p>At Outdoorsmans, we have a long history of using optics on a tripod as a way to pursue game. In fact, some of us were there when it happened for the first time. Roughly 30 years later, after creating the toughest (and only) tripod heads ever made for hunters, we, along with our partners at Rim Country Manufacturing, took on a new challenge–building the perfect tripod head for optics. The Outdoorsmans Fluid Head is the culmination of 30 years of glassing experience, much more machining experience, and breakthroughs in design.</p>
